<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Chunglam Van akhun taksa te'n la a sau,
 A Lalpen-uh angah Lallukhuk kawih tha'n;
 Lei chung lungkham lauhna, gitlohna nusie'n,
 Tatsa mithieng te'n nawpna la thak a sau.

[V2]
 Belam No pakin,
 Kalvari-a thah a um kha;
 Belam No pakin,
 Kumsawt a dinga hingkit chu!

[V3]
 2. Aw Hehpihna la maktak chuh a kim tai,
 Sana belhbu haw gimlim in a dim tai;
 Gitloh zieka thi Lalpa thokit vangin,
 Pathien tawh kumsawt in vaihawm zing tai tiu.

[V4]
 3. A puon uh sawpngim te mai tel thei un au,
 Lungsiet ziek maiin la chuh sa thei un au;
 Gitloh apat Hukdampan ei silthieng tai,
 Kipahna la lopi chuh tun sa tai tiu.</lyrics>
<title>THEY SING A NEW SONG</title>
<author>Thup. 5 :12</author>
<hymn_number>360</hymn_number>
</song>